      "comment": "HIERARCHY mode (the DEFAULT rename.overrideScope=hierarchy) — the standard IDE refactor. Renames URI::urn::canonical across the whole override family: the base URI.pm def, the sibling-branch override (_generic.pm), AND `URI->new(...)->canonical` call sites corpus-wide (CGI.pm, Plack/Request.pm). Edge-gated over @ISA: unrelated same-named methods (Mojo::Path::canonical, PPI::Token) stay OUT.",
